platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: If you ever see a group of teenagers (or twenty- or thirtysomethings) filming themselves doing literally anything, know this: Theyre probably making a video to share on TikTok. Its infinite scroll of new videos combines perfectly edited lip-synching, hilarious sketches, and mesmerizing dance moves with delightful special effects and filters. Its hard not to fall in love with everyones fluffy pets, awkward parents, impressive glow-ups, fails of every kind, and songs and pop-culture references that spark a million memes.
